            "title": "原油直線拉升，布油升超4%突破106美元！特朗普警告將猛烈打擊伊朗",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月2日，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特朗普\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>警告將在未來數周對伊朗將開展猛烈打擊，原油價格直線拉升！倫敦布倫特原油期貨盤中一度突破106美元/桶，日內升幅達4%，創下近兩周新高。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KEwLyhxpQ5WBYRZLJYJ_cA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/acc639926d89004587b20f24d93af538\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">WTI原油期貨價格同步走高，一度站上104美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"578\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YsZXuzZ_Rdw9xhNptD8xdw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/d844d113d26272f5175ae445105bb134\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，香港時間4月2日早上9時（美東周三晚9點），美國總統特朗普就伊朗戰事發表全美電視講話。特朗普在講話中自行宣稱對伊朗戰事取得「快速、決定性、壓倒性勝利」，「未來兩到三周內，我們將對他們進行極其猛烈的打擊……同時，談判也在進行。」 此番表態釋放出「邊打邊談」的信號，進一步加劇了市場對中東局勢升級的擔憂，推動油價短線沖高。<br/><br/></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>4</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股嚟咗啦！邊啲個股有入選？依家訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>唔好錯過啦</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5d1jfNO4QTCnjmB.gZwiKA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/d7f39c6b734627e4db23dd0c862ca74f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><br/><br/></p></blockquote></div>",
