        {
            "title": "川普演講暗示伊朗局勢升級 黃金四連漲終結",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lfY.v1KNPzeLzvg7PT.XEA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/99c9e7171f1ff29af32c5ceb826611ca_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四亞洲交易時段,黃金價格下跌,結束了四個交易日的連漲走勢,投資者對美國總統川普就伊朗衝突發出的新一輪升級信號作出反應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間22:21(北京時間02:21),現貨黃金下跌1.4%,至每盎司4,693.12美元,此前在交易時段早些時候曾攀升至4,800.58美元/盎司的高點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國黃金期貨下跌近2%,至4,721.80美元/盎司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在電視講話中表示,美國將在未來\"兩到三週\"內加強對伊朗的軍事行動,重申華盛頓阻止德黑蘭獲得核武器的立場,市場情緒隨之轉變。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4d1cf8f1-ceff-332e-9268-9542159d0901-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們將在未來兩到三週內對他們進行極其猛烈的打擊。我們將把他們打回到他們應該待的石器時代,\"川普說。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這番言論標誌著本週早些時候立場的逆轉,當時川普曾表示,美國可能在類似的時間框架內離開伊朗,即使沒有正式協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場對圍繞該衝突的言論變化保持高度敏感,投資者正在重新評估地緣政治風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普總統發表演講後,油價反彈,加劇了對通脹壓力的擔憂,這可能使利率維持在高位,並限制黃金等無收益資產的吸引力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元在連續兩個交易日下跌後上漲,使得持有其他貨幣的投資者購買黃金的成本上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者還在等待週五公布的美國就業數據,以尋找聯準會政策前景的線索,這仍然是黃金的關鍵驅動因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在其他貴金屬方面,白銀價格下跌3.2%,至每盎司72.77美元,而鉑金下跌1.7%,至1,934.60美元/盎司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%BC%94%E8%AC%9B%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%9B%9B%E9%80%A3%E6%BC%B2%E7%B5%82%E7%B5%90-033039633.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 11:48:45",
